festival.introText:
After the massive success of Groovebox Festival 2022 and Groovebox Open Air at Nottingham Racecourse, they're back for another year BIGGER & BETTER...

 

Expect a hefty all-day affair with some of the best names in the industry, incredible production, and an unmissable experience all wrapped up in one incredible day...

reviews.title: Review of 4NX Presents Groovebox festival 2022
reviews.body: Worst event I've ever attended. No answer from organisers when asking questions prior to event yet they send you spam messages all the time no problem. To buy anything in the bar first you had to queue to top up your wristband, then you had to wait in another line to the bar. Anything credit left unspent on your wristband is lost - scammy tactics and a steal. Sound system was so bad it was unbelievable for an event hosting big names like Idris Elba. Music was basically commercial crap but that's just mine opinion - i bet most people didn't mind it.

reviews.title: Review of 4NX Presents Groovebox festival 2022
reviews.body:
Brought up in the golden age of festivals, it does feel like there are no new ideas with songs, with just reh**hed old songs.
the drug use was in your face and the end of the evening turned into a complete free for all for taxis which put a damper on the end.

reviews.title: Review of 4NX Presents Groovebox festival 2022
reviews.body: needed more toilets in VIP n more toilet roll in all toilets but everything else was great

faqs.question: When is Groovebox Festival 2023?
faqs.answer: Groovebox takes place Saturday 27th May 2023 (Bank Holiday Weekend)

faqs.question: What happens if I cant attend?
faqs.answer:
Unfortunately, Groovebox cannot issue you with a refund if you cannot make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out.
In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent. Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase.

faqs.question: Where is Groovebox Festival 2023?
faqs.answer: Groovebox will be held in the incredible surroundings of Nottingham Racecourse, Colwick Country Park – approximately a 5-10 minute taxi from Nottingham City Centre.

faqs.question: Whats included with the VIP Tickets?
faqs.answer:
A VIP ticket includes:

VIP fast track entry

Luxury toilets

VIP area

VIP bars

VIP chill out area

faqs.question: Are there any age restrictions at Groovebox?
faqs.answer: Groovebox Festival is a strictly 18+ event with government ID required for all attendees.

faqs.question: Can I bring my own food or drink?
faqs.answer: No, once you are inside there is plenty of bars and food vendors to keep you stocked up throughout the day.
